Package io.github.jgame.net.udp

Class VerifyPacket

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.jgame.net.udp.VerifyPacket
  • public class VerifyPacket
extends java.lang.Object
    Implementation of basic TCP functionality in a sense that the datagram is sent again after a delay if we do not hear back from the server. With exponential backoff.

      • hasSent

      • terminate

        private volatile boolean terminate
        Set this flag if the packet needs to be terminated. No matter what, the VerifyPacket would terminate if this flag is set.
